Intended Usage: FRED is open source domain registry system that includes RDAP server. This RDAP server provides some extended features defined in specification.

This extension describes best practice for result
      set paging.

This extension describes a best practice for
        structuring entity identifiers to enable query bootstrapping.
This extension describes a method that a server can use to return RDAP data along with a redirect response.

This extension describes best practice for result
      set sorting.
